<HEADLINE>
FT  16 DEC 94 / London Stock Exchange: New highs and lows for 1994
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
NEW HIGHS (23).
DIVERSIFIED INDLS (1) Hawtin, ELECTRICITY (4) Midlands, Seeboard, South
